  "about": {
    "intro1": "Interactive map viewer for the **SNCF Signalisation Permanente** (Fixed Signaling) open dataset, with [OpenStreetMap](https://www.openstreetmap.org/) integration. Signals can be exported as OSM tags to the clipboard or via [JOSM Remote Control](https://josm.openstreetmap.de/wiki/Help/Preferences/RemoteControl).",
